# Precaution: keep template layout intact

When editing files under `src/`:

- Do not refactor component structure, section composition, or responsiveness.
- Do not change section order in `src/App.jsx` unless explicitly requested.
- Do not rewrite Tailwind layout class intent (`flex/grid` + breakpoints like `max-lg`, `max-xl`, `sm`, `wide`) or shared utilities (`padding*`, `max-container`).

Allowed changes are limited to rebrand surfaces:
- copy/links/data (often `src/constants/index.js`)
- images/icons/logos (`src/assets/*`)
- safe token-level changes (`tailwind.config.js`) that preserve class usage patterns
